# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# vLLM DGX Spark Configuration — Gemma 4 26B-A4B (MoE)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# MoE model: 26B total / 3.8B active params (128 experts). Apache 2.0 license.
# BF16 weight footprint ≈ 52 GB (fits single B200 110 GB with ample KV room).
# Strengths: #6 open model on Arena AI, 97% of dense 31B quality at fraction
#            of compute, 85 tok/s on consumer hardware, 256K context,
#            native multimodal (text + image + video), function calling,
#            configurable thinking mode. Latency-optimized variant.
# Released: 2026-04-02
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Required for Multi-Node                                                 │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
WORKER_HOST="${WORKER_HOST:-}"
WORKER_IB_IP="${WORKER_IB_IP:-}"
WORKER_USER="${WORKER_USER:-$(whoami)}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Model Settings                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
MODEL="${MODEL:-google/gemma-4-26B-A4B-it}"

# Single B200 — 26B MoE fits BF16 on one GPU with lots of headroom
TENSOR_PARALLEL="${TENSOR_PARALLEL:-1}"

# ~52 GB weights leaves ~47 GB for KV cache — excellent headroom
GPU_MEMORY_UTIL="${GPU_MEMORY_UTIL:-0.90}"

# Generous context; ample KV cache budget allows large windows
MAX_MODEL_LEN="${MAX_MODEL_LEN:-131072}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Docker Settings                                                         │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_IMAGE="${VLLM_IMAGE:-nvcr.io/nvidia/vllm:26.03-py3}"
HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME="${HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-head}"
WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME="${WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-worker}"
SHM_SIZE="${SHM_SIZE:-16g}"
RAY_VERSION="${RAY_VERSION:-2.54.0}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Network Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_PORT="${VLLM_PORT:-8000}"
RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT="${RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT:-8265}"
RAY_PORT="${RAY_PORT:-6385}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Storage Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_CACHE="${HF_CACHE:-/raid/hf-cache}"
WORKER_HF_CACHE="${WORKER_HF_CACHE:-${HF_CACHE}}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Authentication                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_TOKEN="${HF_TOKEN:-}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ vLLM Options                                                            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
# MoE model — enable expert parallelism
ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL="${ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL:-true}"

SWAP_SPACE="${SWAP_SPACE:-16}"
TRUST_REMOTE_CODE="${TRUST_REMOTE_CODE:-false}"
LOAD_FORMAT="${LOAD_FORMAT:-safetensors}"

# No quantization needed — BF16 fits easily; enable tool calling
EXTRA_ARGS="--enable-auto-tool-choice --tool-call-parser hermes"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ NCCL/InfiniBand Settings (auto-detected, override if needed)            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
NCCL_DEBUG="${NCCL_DEBUG:-WARN}"
